# Title: Email Exifiltration Via Powershell
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems),  Azure-Sentinel (idea)
# Date: 2022-09-09
# Level: high
# Description: Detects email exfiltration via powershell cmdlets
# MITRE Tactic: Exfiltration
# Tags: attack.exfiltration
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_powershell_email_exfil.yml

CommandLine="*Add-PSSnapin*" CommandLine="*Get-Recipient*" CommandLine="*-ExpandProperty*" CommandLine="*EmailAddresses*" CommandLine="*SmtpAddress*" CommandLine="*-hidetableheaders*" Image IN ("*\\powershell.exe", "*\\pwsh.exe")